WEBVTT

00:02.001 --> 00:03.336
You have to admit
we're really good together.

00:03.404 --> 00:05.304
Yes, yes we are!

00:07.740 --> 00:09.908
I let Chase put a claim in
on Dexter

00:09.975 --> 00:12.210
and Ty was right there.

00:12.278 --> 00:14.212
Any reason I should worried
about my boyfriend

00:14.280 --> 00:16.915
giving my best friend
such expensive gifts?

00:16.982 --> 00:18.050
It wasn't a gift.

00:18.117 --> 00:19.551
I was gonna do some clinics
with him.

00:19.618 --> 00:21.053
What're you doing?

00:21.120 --> 00:23.320
Amy and I called it quits.

00:25.000 --> 00:31.074
